nowledge co-production and agricultural co-management are emerging in developing world.•Knowledge co-production was effective on identifying proper adaptive strategies in Iran.•Natural, financial and structural constraints reduced adoption of adaptive strategies.•Co-produced knowledge enhanced water efficiency and resilience under water scarcity.},
